931
01:17:47,119 --> 01:17:52,505
Isto em poucas semanas...
Hipccup teria passado de... ser um...

932
01:17:52,531 --> 01:17:53,531
Hiccup.

933
01:17:59,382 --> 01:18:02,214
Quero dizer, eu os teria amarrado a
