989
01:25:51,466 --> 01:25:53,139
Não o magoem.

990
01:25:53,165 --> 01:25:55,166
Para trás.

991
01:26:00,252 --> 01:26:01,252
Tu.

992
01:26:14,916 --> 01:26:16,678
Nós vamos com os outros.

993
01:26:23,297 --> 01:26:24,442
Devias saber.

994
01:26:24,468 --> 01:26:24,768
Pai.

995
01:26:24,793 --> 01:26:25,792
