1083
01:32:16,809 --> 01:32:17,809
Obrigado, cop.

1084
01:32:19,326 --> 01:32:21,630
Quanto tempo achas que vamos andar?

1085
01:32:32,690 --> 01:32:34,371
Afasta-te, Draugr.

1086
