1142
01:40:28,714 --> 01:40:30,824
Perfeito para esmagar e esmagar.

1143
01:40:30,872 --> 01:40:32,974
Olhos pequenos, narinas grandes.

1144
01:40:33,111 --> 01:40:35,032
